Package com.hannesdorfmann.mosby.mvp.viewstate.lce

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LceViewState<D,V extends MvpLceView<D>>
    An LCE (Loading-Content-Error) ViewState is a viewstate that can save and restore loading, the content, or the error (exception).
    ParcelableLceViewState<D,V extends MvpLceView<D>>
    A common interface for LceViewState and RestorableParcelableViewState.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbsLceViewState<D,V extends MvpLceView<D>>
    A base view state implementation for LceViewState (Loading-Content-Error)
    AbsParcelableLceViewState<D,V extends MvpLceView<D>>
    Extends AbsLceViewState by implementing RestorableViewState.
    MvpLceViewStateActivity<CV extends View,M,V extends MvpLceView<M>,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    A MvpLceActivity with ViewState support.
    MvpLceViewStateFragment<CV extends View,M,V extends MvpLceView<M>,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
    A MvpLceFragment with ViewState support.
